<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="th">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>ระบบจัดการบ่อเลี้ยงปลา - คณะประมง</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.1/font/bootstrap-icons.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Sarabun:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    * {
      font-family: 'Sarabun', sans-serif;
    }
    body {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a5f2a 0%, #2d8a4e 50%, #1a5f2a 100%);
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    .landing-container {
      flex: 1;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .landing-card {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 40px;
      text-align: center;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
      cursor: pointer;
      min-height: 320px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .landing-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-10px);
      box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    }
    .landing-card .icon-wrapper {
      width: 120px;
      height: 120px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .landing-card:hover .icon-wrapper {
      transform: scale(1.1);
    }
    .landing-card .icon-wrapper i {
      font-size: 60px;
      color: white;
    }
    .landing-card.pond .icon-wrapper {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0d6efd, #0dcaf0);
    }
    .landing-card.equipment .icon-wrapper {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fd7e14, #ffc107);
    }
    .landing-card h3 {
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: #333;
    }
    .landing-card p {
      color: #666;
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }
    .landing-card .btn-enter {
      margin-top: 20px;
      padding: 10px 30px;
      font-weight: 600;
      border-radius: 50px;
    }
    .landing-card.pond .btn-enter {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0d6efd, #0dcaf0);
      border: none;
      color: white;
    }
    .landing-card.equipment .btn-enter {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fd7e14, #ffc107);
      border: none;
      color: white;
    }
    .header-section {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 30px 20px;
    }
    .header-section h1 {
      color: white;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    }
    .header-section p {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
    }
    .admin-link {
      position: fixed;
      bottom: 20px;
      right: 20px;
    }
    .footer-section {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header-section">
    <h1><i class="bi bi-water me-2"></i>ระบบจัดการบ่อเลี้ยงปลา</h1>
    <p class="mb-0">คณะประมง มหาวิทยาลัยเกษตรศาสตร์</p>
  </div>

  <div class="landing-container">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center g-4">
        <div class="col-md-5 col-lg-4">
          <a href="/pond" class="text-decoration-none">
            <div class="landing-card pond">
              <div class="icon-wrapper">
                <i class="bi bi-droplet-half"></i>
              </div>
              <h3>บ่อเลี้ยงปลา</h3>
              <p>ดูผังบ่อ จองบ่อ<br>ตรวจสอบสถานะการใช้งาน</p>
              <button class="btn btn-enter">
                <i class="bi bi-arrow-right-circle me-2"></i>เข้าสู่ระบบบ่อ
              </button>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-5 col-lg-4">
          <a href="/equipment" class="text-decoration-none">
            <div class="landing-card equipment">
              <div class="icon-wrapper">
                <i class="bi bi-tools"></i>
              </div>
              <h3>ยืม-คืน อุปกรณ์</h3>
              <p>ยืมอุปกรณ์ ตรวจสอบสถานะ<br>แจ้งคืนอุปกรณ์</p>
              <button class="btn btn-enter">
                <i class="bi bi-arrow-right-circle me-2"></i>เข้าสู่ระบบอุปกรณ์
              </button>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="footer-section">
    <small>ระบบจัดการบ่อเลี้ยงปลา - คณะประมง</small>
  </div>

  <a href="/admin/login" class="admin-link btn btn-light btn-sm shadow">
    <i class="bi bi-person-circle me-1"></i>สำหรับเจ้าหน้าที่
  </a>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
